The paper discusses a searchable encryption scheme that addresses security and privacy concerns in cloud computing. This topic is closely related to computer security (cs.CR), database systems (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel scheme that integrates machine learning methods, which is also relevant to computer communications (cs.CC).
